Calculated: derive from location_latitude and location_longitude using derive_last_changed_at function. Backend compares current position with previous position. If latitude or longitude changed (threshold applied to filter GPS noise), sets timestamp to now(). Used for dwell-time calculations and 'parked since X' features.

Pseudo code:
if (current.lat !== previous.lat || current.lng !== previous.lng) {
  distance = calculateDistance(current, previous)
  if (distance > threshold) {
    location_last_changed_at = now()
  }
}

